item.title: CVE-2023-32337|2024-08-02T15:10:24.948Z -- ibm -- maximo%20spatial%20asset%20management
item.description: IBM Maximo Spatial Asset Management 8.10 is vulnerable to server-side request forgery (SSRF). This may allow an authenticated attacker to send unauthorized requests from the system, potentially leading to network enumeration or facilitating other attacks. IBM X-Force ID: 255288.
